      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Owing to its possible interfer-\nence with the overhead electrical\nwork now in progress, the 100000\nclub excursion to Moscow, Idaho,\non the new line of the Spokane &\nInland will not be run on Septem-\nDer Is as originally intended. A\ncommittee of the club visited the\nInland Empire offices today in re-\ngard to the matter and were in\nformed that the excursion could\nnot be run on the date set without\nseriously interfering with the con-\nstruction now being rushed with\nall possible speed.\n\n\n1t may be arranged to run the\nexcursion on September 3d. Super\nintendent Bowdish will determine\nthis after a trip over the line to-\nmorrow."
    }
